myVelibCore.stationPackage

Class ParkingSlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • myVelibCore.stationPackage.ParkingSlot

  • public class ParkingSlot
extends java.lang.Object
    Parking slots are linked to stations. They can contain bycicles

    A parking slot is characterized by :

    • A status (available or not)
    • A unique ID
    • Possibly a bycicle
    • A station
    Author:
    Edouard Benauw
